Package: vlm-edge-studio
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Maintainer: NXP
Architecture: arm64
Depends: rt-sdk-ara2
Description: VLM Edge Studio - Vision Language Model Application
  Features:
    - Supported SoC: i.MX 8M Plus FRDM, i.MX 95 FRDM
    - User-friendly GUI for model selection and prompt submission
    - Real-time streaming token responses via Server-Sent Events (SSE)
    - Integration with eIQ AAF Connector for HTTP-based communication
    - Support for Qwen2.5 VL 7B model for Video/Image understanding
    - Support USBC HD Camera for Video Recording/ Image Capture
